title: Marvel NOW Week of 11-19-2014 (darkhomr)
description:
Welcome to the 2014 version of Marvel NOW!  Week after week I will be bringing you the latest in comics in the Marvel NOW universe as well as the All-New Marvel NOW stories.  Can you believe we are in the Marvel NOW and they are putting out an ALL NEW version of the titles?  What will NOT be included is Disney stuff, TV stuff, Ultimate Universe, and kids books. 



This weeks' release (November 19, 2014) includes 23 issues with 1 new #1s (Spider-Woman)


My release packs are as follows: 


DC Universe 52 (Wednesdays based on scanners release times, but not later than Friday morning)
Marvel NOW! (Marvel Comics in the NOW! universe will be released Wednesdays, based on scanners release times)
